	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ausgezeichnet! <delay20 />Exzellent!<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Aber sag, <delay8 />Schätzchen, <delay8 />du scheinst
