	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Es beruhigt mich zu wissen,<delay8 /> dass <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x11 0xcd00 0x8 0x6d 0x65 0x69 0x6e 0xa 0x6d 0x65 0x69 0x6e 0x65 0x8 0x6d 0x65 0x69 0x6e" /> <tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> in guten Händen sein wird.</message>
